Homepage: https://github.com/miketsukerman/relay-tools
Description: Tooling for Waveshare Raspberry Pi relay hats
 relay-tools provides CLI utilities and an HTTP API for controlling
 Waveshare Raspberry Pi relay hats.
 .
 It supports the Waveshare RPi Relay Board (B) and provides:
  - Direct relay control commands (on, off, toggle, status)
  - A FastAPI-based HTTP API daemon
  - A systemd service unit for automatic startup
